features: WIDE COMPATIBILITY: XINLEI rolling TV stand can fit most 13" to 50" flat or curved TV screens or monitors with VESA 75x75mm to 200x200mm, hold up to 20kg. Including Samsung, Vizio, LG, TCL, Hisense and etc.

TILT: This TV floor stand can tilt your TV up by 30°and down 10°according to your sitting posture to reduce glare and improve the viewing experience. Perfect for gym, office, home, studio, exhibition hall, trade show, kitchen.
HEIGHT ADJUSTMENT: Featuring unlimited point adjustable height, max height 52.95”. The TV mount stand allows you to position the screen closer to eye level for better viewing experience.

SPACE SAVING: The front long and back short leg base design not only increase stability, but also allows it to get a closer distance from the wall, so you can place it in the back of the cabinet to save space.
MOVABLE: You to easily move the TV from room to room or swivel, and with lockable casters to ensure safety. No drilling process is needed, easy to install.
description: Product Description Height Adjustable The height of the TV can be adjusted as you need up to 52.95" without limited point . Tilt Adjustment You can reduce glare by tilt the TV, and tilt up 30° is perfect for some reading console. Base Construction This TV cart is durable and stable with the centre of balance in the middle. Save Space The distance to the wall is only 2 ", which is very suitable for narrow small rooms.
